### GameController Tests

# Create a new game
POST http://localhost:7777/games
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "id": "game1",
  "name": "Chess",
  "owner": "user1",
  "players": []
}

### Add a player to a game
POST http://localhost:7777/games/game1/players
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "id": "player1",
  "name": "John Doe"
}

### Remove a player from a game
DELETE http://localhost:7777/games/game1/players/player1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Remove a game
DELETE http://localhost:7777/games/game1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Get game info
GET http://localhost:7777/games/game1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Get all games by owner
GET http://localhost:7777/games/owner/user1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

