### InvitationController Tests

# Send an invitation
POST http://localhost:7777/invitations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "senderId": "user1",
  "receiverId": "user2",
  "gameId": "game1",
  "status": "pending"
}

### Get received invitations
GET http://localhost:7777/invitations/received/user2
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Get sent invitations
GET http://localhost:7777/invitations/sent/user1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Update invitation status
PUT http://localhost:7777/invitations/1/status?status=accepted
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}